                <h2 class="heading01">Payment Processing Services</h2>
                <h2 class="heading01 pad-top-none">Our Role</h2>

                <p>The Services allow Clients to pay and Professionals to accept fees, including Card-based payments initiated with Cards bearing the trademarks of MasterCard International Inc. and Visa Inc. Hair Decoded helps the processing of payments Professionals receive from Clients. This means that we collect, analyze and relay information generated in connection with these payments.</p>
