                <p>We may choose not to authorize any transaction that you submit to us if we believe in our sole discretion that the transaction is in violation of this Agreement, or that it exposes Professionals, other Hair Decoded Users, the PSP or Hair Decoded to harm. If we reasonably suspect that your Account has been used for an unauthorized, illegal, or criminal purpose, you give us express authorization to share information about you, your Account, and any of your transactions with law enforcement. You hereby agree to provide us with information and assistance in a timely manner and acknowledge that payment in connection with a suspicious transaction may be delayed until such transaction has been cleared by Hair Decoded.</p>
