                <p>As a result to the payout schedule identified below, we will deposit amounts received by us for transactions you submit through the Services (less any applicable Fees) to your verified bank account.</p>
                <p>If the bank account you link to your Account is incorrect and Hair Decoded is not able to debit or credit the bank account, the bank account will be de-linked from your Account. Funds will be deposited only when the transaction is deemed complete. Transactions will be deemed complete when we have received or sent the funds and when we or the financial institutions have accepted the funds.</p>

                <h2 class="heading01">Standard Schedule of Payouts</h2>
                <p>Upon validation of your US bank account, and verifying that you have ten dollars or more in your Account, Hair Decoded will automatically initiate a payout to your bank account at the end of every business day. If the payment is received before 4pm Pacific Time, the payout to your bank account will usually fund the next business day.</p>

