                <p>In the event that in a given calendar year you receive more than $20,000 in gross amount of payments and more than 200 payments, Hair Decoded will make a report to the IRS, as required by law, your name, address, Tax Identification Number, or EIN, the total dollar amount of the payments you receive in a calendar year.</p>
