                <p>If there your Account is inactive for at least two years, consecutively, and you have a balance, we will notify you by sending an email and give you the option of keeping your Account open and maintaining or withdrawing the balance. If you do not respond to our notice within thirty days, we will automatically close your Account and escheat your funds in accordance with applicable law and if permitted to Hair Decoded.</p>
